description: Bill Gates is behind this entire thing. I told you guys satan has an army too and it’s the 1%. If this shutdown doesn’t end soon, this will be the end of the economy as we know it. But do not fear these trials that are coming because many miracles are coming from the Heavenly Father like NEVER before! While you’re seeing this world fall apart, you will also see many souls being saved and many revivals. Mark my words! NO......FEAR!!! ONLY.....FAITH! #hollyweirdisevil
